# Project Context

This project is a small English center management system.

Core goal:
- Real daily operation.
- Simple and easy to use.
- Friendly for a teacher/admin.
- One user role only.
- Accuracy is more important than fancy architecture.

Do not optimize for:
- Portfolio complexity.
- Enterprise architecture.
- Microservices.
- Event-driven architecture.
- Multiple roles/permissions.

Tech stack:
Backend:
- Java 21
- Spring Boot
- Spring Web MVC
- Spring Data JPA
- Spring Validation
- Spring Security simple login
- MySQL
- Flyway

Frontend:
- React
- TypeScript
- Vite
- Ant Design
- React Router
- TanStack Query
- Axios
- dayjs

Architecture:
- Modular monolith.
- Backend and frontend in the same workspace.
- No API Gateway.
- No RabbitMQ/Kafka.
- No complex role permission.

